생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕 💦 템플릿 고르기 
💦 배포방법 
💦 permission denied? 
💦 github action…]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/TID/블로그를-만들기-까지.../</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/TID/블로그를-만들기-까지.../</guid><pubDate>Thu, 05 Nov 2020 23:12:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;오늘 드디어 블로그를 만들게 되었다.&lt;br&gt;
생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#template&quot;&gt;템플릿 고르기&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#deploy&quot;&gt;배포방법&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#denied&quot;&gt;permission denied?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#gitaction&quot;&gt;github action&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;template&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-템플릿-고르기-jekyll-vs-gatsby&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A5%B4%EA%B8%B0-jekyll-vs-gatsby&quot; aria-label=&quot; 템플릿 고르기 jekyll vs gatsby permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 템플릿 고르기 Jekyll vs Gatsby&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;선택 장애가 있어 템플릿을 고를 때부터 머리가 아팠다.
거두절미하고 Jekyll &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;minimal-mistakes&lt;/code&gt; 와 Gatsby &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt;가 최종 선택지였다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;minimal-mistakes는&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#minimal-mistakes%EB%8A%94&quot; aria-label=&quot;minimal mistakes는 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;minimal-mistakes는…&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;해당 템블릿 기준으로 저장소 생성부터 광고 붙이기까지 참고할만한 &lt;a href=&quot;https://devinlife.com/howto/#1-github-pages-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%94%B0%EB%9D%BC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;블로그 글&lt;/a&gt;이 있다.
하지만 페이지 렌더링마다 깜빡거림이 심했고 Jekyll이 나에게는 꽤 귀찮아 보였다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;gatsby-starter-bee는&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#gatsby-starter-bee%EB%8A%94&quot; aria-label=&quot;gatsby starter bee는 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;gatsby-starter-bee는…&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;페이지를 렌더링 할 때마다 깜빡거리지 않고 pc는 물론 mobile 반응형 화면까지 깔끔하다.
그리고 배포도 간단해보였다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;그래서-블로그-템블릿으로-code-classlanguage-textgatsby-starter-beecode를-선택하게-되었다&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EC%84%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%ED%85%9C%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%BF%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-code-classlanguage-textgatsby-starter-beecode%EB%A5%BC-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%ED%95%98%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%98%EC%97%88%EB%8B%A4&quot; aria-label=&quot;그래서 블로그 템블릿으로 code classlanguage textgatsby starter beecode를 선택하게 되었다 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;그래서 블로그 템블릿으로 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt;를 선택하게 되었다.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;deploy&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-배포방법-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages&quot; aria-label=&quot; 배포방법 publish with netlify vs github pages permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 배포방법 Publish with netlify vs github pages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee#-gatsby-config&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/a&gt; 에서 배포는 netlify와 github pages 두가지 배포방법을 제시해놓았다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.outsider.ne.kr/1417&quot;&gt;netlify&lt;/a&gt;는 서버 없이 쉽게 정적페이지를 배포해주는 도구라고한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;denied&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-permission-denied&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-permission-denied&quot; aria-label=&quot; permission denied permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 permission denied&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;/content/assets/profile.png&quot; alt=&quot;error-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;gitaction&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-github-action으로-gh-pages-배포하기&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-github-action%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-gh-pages-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&quot; aria-label=&quot; github action으로 gh pages 배포하기 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 github action으로 gh-pages 배포하기&lt;/h3&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[about]]></title><description><![CDATA[김연화 🥑]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/resume-en/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com/resume-en/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 27 Jan 2019 16:21:13 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h1 id=&quot;김연화&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%EA%B9%80%EC%97%B0%ED%99%94&quot; aria-label=&quot;김연화 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt